                Audi me <supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>ud<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> tamen <lb n="2"/>quem secu<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>dus</abbr></expan> bibes hic vasi <expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">def</supplied>er</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan>
